text: Brian Murray may refer to: *Brian Murray (actor) (1937–2018), South African actor and director *Brian Murray (governor) (1921–1991), Governor of Victoria, Deputy Chief of the Royal Australian Navy *Brian Murray (Gaelic footballer), Donegal player *Brian Murray (hurler) (born 1984), Limerick player *Brian Murray (judge), Irish judge and former barrister *Brian Murray (politician), American state legislator in the Massachusetts House of Representatives. ==See also== *Brian Doyle-Murray (born 1945), actor *Bryan Murray (disambiguation)
